		===================================
		librfsctl - RedirFS Control Library
			       README
		===================================

This software is distributed under the Boost Software License, Version 1.0.

1. Introduction

	RedirFS Control Library is a userspace library, which provides interface
	for basic management of filters registered to the RedirFS Framework. It
	is based on the sysfs interface provided by RedirFS.

	For an overview of the RedirFS project, visit 

		http://www.redirfs.org

2. Installation

	See the INSTALL file.

3. Documentation

	http://www.redirfs.org/tiki-index.php?page=redirfs_doc

4. Problems & Bugs
	
	http://www.redirfs.org/cgi-bin/bugzilla/index.cgi
